/v/t64.5771-25/39035422_617153453816929_8197618131681588935_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=dit7OKwb9PQQ7kNvgHdEsYQ&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB_cgRD86PSZQ7vI3c0QqPkwU_ltK3gPWFR1sLRTSK47Q&oe=67262A29"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "TBC_Landscape.png", "id": "1933231860214727", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036614_1933231863548060_6384280158781549633_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=waNfUxkTPy4Q7kNvgHmHuvn&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA39Wv6EZADX59E3IQOxuczilsM9v65DRutrcsrQG42jw&oe=672606CB"}, "display_name": "Tube Be Continued", "keywords": ["puzzle", "funny", "cute", "story", "pet"], "long_description": "\u2b50 Play 136 hamster-approved puzzles across 60 levels! \u2b50\n\nHello! Welcome to TUBE Industries: a hamster owned and operated tube puzzle emporium! \n\nPrepare for a tube-based, puzzle-filled, HAM-PACKED adventure with our charismatic leader: The BOSS. Here at TUBE Industries we provide the puzzles and you provide\u2026 the brains. No shady business here!\n\nTUBE-Based Benefits:\n\u2022 60 levels across 3 themed floors: Hamster Hangout, Smart Home Slide & Bakery Blitz!\n\u2022 Customize your hamster\u2019s appearance!\n\u2022 Classic and slide-based tube puzzles!\n\u2022 Numerous Mini-Puzzles including our new hamster cannon!\n\u2022 Chat with the BOSS and help him deal with important \u201cbusiness decisions\u201d!\n\u2022 Relaxed-pace gameplay with no time pressure.\n\u2022 Supports seated, standing, or room scale play.\n\nYour destination for TUBE-Based entertainment awaits!\n\nSincerely,\nThe BOSS", "short_description": "\u2b50 Play 136 hamster-approved puzzles across 60 levels! \u2b50\n\nHello! Welcome to TUBE Industries: a hamster owned and operated tube puzzle emporium! \n\nPrepare for a tube-based, puzzle-filled, HAM-PACKED adventure with our charismatic leader: The BOSS. Here at TUBE Industries we 